<br>
<br>
Would also like to add:<br>
1: Improved Flying kick. <br>
Either more damage, or more frequent. And for krickey's sake, what is up with 92's in Ssra? =)<br>
<br>
2: Paralellism (9 points): <br>
This ability disconnects your special monk attacks, making them available independently of each other<br>
<br>
3: Vigilance:<br>
This ability gives the monk the ability to use all his defencive skills from all angles.<br>
<br>
<br>
Other: Correct the flaws in our current disciplines. I've been lvl 60 for allmost 2 years now, and still I have yet to see Silent fist do more than 300 damage. Also, either extend the time on some of the discs, such as inner flame, or the innate haste disc that I've used so often I don't even remember it's name, or reduce the refresh timer on them significantly.<br>
